Rating: 4
I love the premise for this salad and have modified it in a variety of ways: (1) I don't cut the kale, but tear it by hand; (2) when serving vegans, I use nutritional yeast instead of cheese; (3) I prefer toasted sesame oil instead of olive for a nuttier taste; (4) I add fresh curly parsley (1/8th of recipe); (5) I sometimes add fresh mint leaves, shredded or sliced for a refreshing pop. Thanks for all the previous comments!

