Rating: 4
Every time I have made this is has been a huge hit and people ask me for the recipe. One tip is that you don't have to soak the currants in a much Balsamic as they say. If you soak them in a really small container, you can use half the amount because they are not spread out along the bottom of a dish. This helps you to discard way less balsamic, if any at all.

